berusia 60 tahun.

145
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:47,610
Kau harus menjaga kesehatanmu!

146
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,380
Kim Mi So!

147
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:53,120
